Amazon Sales Analytics Dashboard (Power BI Project)
Tools & Technologies: Power BI, Excel, DAX, Data Modeling, Visualization

Description:
Developed a comprehensive and interactive Power BI dashboard to analyze Amazon sales data and uncover key performance insights across time, product categories, and customer feedback.

Key Contributions:

Time-Based Performance Metrics:

Calculated Year-to-Date (YTD) Sales, Quarter-to-Date (QTD) Sales, and Weekly Sales using advanced DAX functions.

Analyzed Monthly Sales Trends to identify seasonality and peak performance periods.

Product Insights:

Measured YTD Product Sold and YTD Customer Reviews to understand product performance and customer satisfaction.

Identified Top Products by YTD Sales and Top Products by YTD Reviews to highlight high-impact items.

Analyzed Sales by Product Category to assess product line contributions and category-wise trends.

Visual Storytelling:

Designed a clean and intuitive dashboard with KPI cards, time-series graphs, bar charts, and slicers for dynamic filtering.

Business Impact:

Enabled strategic insights into top-performing products, review volume, and temporal sales trends.

Facilitated informed decision-making for marketing, inventory, and customer engagement strategies.

